(Republished)

National Gypsum Company, Respondent, v. Eljam Mason Supply, Inc., Appellant.

Order entered March 3, 1969, and judgment entered March 12, 1969, unanimously affirmed, with $50 costs and disbursements to respondent. No opinion. Concur — Eager, J. P., Capozzoli, McGivern, McNally and Steuer, JJ.
